Usage: gh-pull-all.mjs [--org <organization> | --user <username>] [options]

Options:
      --version            Show version number                         [boolean]
  -o, --org                GitHub organization name                     [string]
  -u, --user               GitHub username                              [string]
  -t, --token              GitHub personal access token (optional for public
                           repos)                                       [string]
  -s, --ssh                Use SSH URLs for cloning (requires SSH key setup)
                                                      [boolean] [default: false]
  -d, --dir                Target directory for repositories
                        [string] [default: "/tmp/gh-issue-solver-1782400949399"]
  -j, --threads            Number of concurrent operations (default: 8)
                                                           [number] [default: 8]
      --single-thread      Run operations sequentially (equivalent to --threads
                           1)                         [boolean] [default: false]
      --live-updates       Enable live in-place status updates (default: true,
                           use --no-live-updates to disable)
                                                       [boolean] [default: true]
      --delete             Delete all cloned repositories (skips repos with
                           uncommitted changes)       [boolean] [default: false]
      --pull-from-default  Pull changes from the default branch (main/master)
                           into the current branch if behind
                                                      [boolean] [default: false]
      --switch-to-default  Switch to the default branch (main/master) in each
                           repository                 [boolean] [default: false]
  -h, --help               Show help                                   [boolean]

Examples:
  gh-pull-all.mjs --org deep-assistant      Sync all repositories from
                                            deep-assistant organization
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard             Sync all repositories from konard
                                            user account
  gh-pull-all.mjs --org myorg --ssh --dir   Clone using SSH to ./repos directory
  ./repos
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard --threads   Use 5 concurrent operations
  5
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard             Run operations sequentially
  --single-thread
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard -j 16       Use 16 concurrent operations (alias
                                            for --threads)
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard             Disable live updates for terminal
  --no-live-updates                         history preservation
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard --delete    Delete all cloned repositories (with
                                            confirmation)
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard             Pull from default branch to current
  --pull-from-default                       branch when behind
  gh-pull-all.mjs --user konard             Switch all repositories to their
  --switch-to-default                       default branch
